title: 820 00163 liquid damage
message: 820 00163, liquid damage around the u7330-u7310 vent area. I cleaned the area with flux and hot air, and ran through ultrasonic. The machine fully boots, but the fans kick on full blast about half way through boot, and the machine is running hot as a firecracker. I first thought the fans maybe a senser issue, but it seems like they are just doing their job trying to cool the machine down. Any advice, im at a loss with this one...

title: 820 00163 liquid damage
message: Replace those power supplies ASAP and maybe the board will be saved. I bet that CPU is damaged, though. See if the unit crashes coming out of (or during) deep sleep and/or under stress. Liquid to that area is not good news.
